<http://ns.inria.fr/iadas/measurementTools-vocab/Factor%201comprises%20the%20following%20varibales%20%3A%20my%20friends%20and%20i%20help%20each%20other%2C%20I%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20do%20the%20same%20things%20as%20my%20friends%2C%20my%20parents%20give%20me%20enough%20money%20for%20my%20expenses%2C%20I%20can%20talk%20to%20my%20parents%20whenever%20I%20need%20to%2C%20my%20parents%20have%20enough%20money%20for%20me%0AFactor%203%20includes%3A%20I%20would%20like%20my%20clothes%20to%20fit%20better%2C%20I%20would%20like%20my%20physique%20to%20be%20different%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20be%20thinner> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Factor 1comprises the following varibales : my friends and i help each other, I have enough money to do the same things as my friends, my parents give me enough money for my expenses, I can talk to my parents whenever I need to, my parents have enough money for me\nFactor 3 includes: I would like my clothes to fit better, I would like my physique to be different, I would like to be thinner" .
